entry.request: PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT ?s WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Black_Parade> dbpedia-owl:abstract ?s FILTER langMatches(lang(?s), 'en') } LIMIT 1
